display.lds42: This collection is stored partially onsite (Series 1-12, 14-31) at Firestone Library and partially offsite (Series 13: Ledgers) at the ReCAP facility. Boxes 73-75; boxes 193-195; boxes 197-199; box 287, folder 9; boxes 768-771; box 772, folders 1-30; box 773, folder 41; boxes 774-779; and box 866, folders 1-3 are stored in special vault facilities.
